        "### Summary of Results and Recommendations\n",
        "\n",
        "**Processed Contacts:** A total of **60** contacts were collected. DNS resolution has been checked for each website, and the 'DNS_Resolves' column indicates the result. These contacts have been prioritized based on their 'Rating' (descending) and 'Organization' name (ascending).\n",
